	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hi everyone,<br><br>I'm lv 3 and I'm trying to max my casting skills. Unfortunately, I run oom quite fast and I spend more time sitting than casting.<br>What +wis gear should I look for at my level to increase mana ?<br><br>Thanks for your answers<br><br>Wanilae<br>Druid of the 3rd Stone<br>Tunare<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
